===[[Pokémon Masters EX]]===
{{main|Plumeria (Masters)}}
Plumeria forms a [[sync pair]] with {{p|Salazzle}} and {{p|Gengar}} in [[Pokémon Masters EX]]. Plumeria became a playable sync pair on March 27, 2020.

Plumeria has also made notable appearances in one of the game's main stories, the [[villain arc]].  

